            PingTester can store a list of IP addresses and network    
           test commands to increase the working efficiency, perform   
          ping and traceroute test by one click, 'ping sweep' subnets  
          or interval ping all the hosts on a list continuously, save  
              the individual ping records to a txt or Excel file,      
           generate statistics reports which group by specified time   
             interval, so that you can know the network connection     
            status of each period. All dos commands can run in the     
                                 Windows form.                         
           The database edition has all features of the professional   
                       edition and has database support:               
           It can real-time input each line of the ping test results   
             to the database, you can use an existed database (SQL     
           Server, Access, ODBC), and define which table and fields    
                 will be used to input the ping test results.          


         INSTALLATiON:
                  Unpack,run, use info from serial.txt, enjoy
